{"tid":2454637,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"綾瀨遙影視兩忙 大露背入戲院宣傳新片","createTime":"2021-03-20T11:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T12:55:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6a0f4df5f01c673b8590eae4f1d47880ad1bc3","tid":2454637,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RxYnVhYHFFJNyKQw-tA6v_OQKsQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MYD2M4REINAIFMK4JDG75TXQQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRxYnVhYHFFJNyKQw-tA6v_OQKsQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMYD2M4REINAIFMK4JDG75TXQQI.jpg&h=02897779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n35歲日本女星綾瀨遙近年主要拍劇，由她夥拍夥拍高橋一生的TBS人氣劇《天國與地獄》昨天在當地播出大結局，綾瀨遙同時有新片上映，令她最佳可謂影視兩忙。<br />\n<br />\n綾瀨遙與西島秀俊合演的2017年大熱劇集《太太，請小心輕放》添食開拍電影版，這部新片原本安排去年6月開畫，可是因疫情影響而被迫押後了將近一年，兩位主角今日現身戲院造勢，還有同片拍檔小日向文世、岡田健史及導演佐藤東彌，而是次活動更在當地115間戲院同時直播。<br />\n<br />\n綾瀨遙今日穿着黑色連身裙大晒玉背，她在《太太，請小心輕放》系列中扮演女特務，與片中丈夫西島秀俊各自有不可告人的神秘身份。今日活動上，大會主持問到眾星在愛情與任務之間如何決擇時，岡田健史就稱貓與狗對他而言已很難選擇，綾瀨遙亦十分認同：「我都一樣，老家有養狗，之後再養多一隻貓，知道兩者各有優點，很難取捨。」她又謂電影遲了一年開畫，很高興終於見到觀眾，希望大家可以入戲院好好享受。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CwXKAKxgx53kFyCF2p9T_OOsrjM=/802x544/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NVAY2KHRDVHU7GMEPQYKTB6HE4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCwXKAKxgx53kFyCF2p9T_OOsrjM%3D%2F802x544%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNVAY2KHRDVHU7GMEPQYKTB6HE4.JPG&h=ce15efc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rv0WY1hgt-6fhn46uPZ_akmgcqU=/802x535/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EK6OVB3AVVGM5IBTCYK626LSDU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRv0WY1hgt-6fhn46uPZ_akmgcqU%3D%2F802x535%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEK6OVB3AVVGM5IBTCYK626LSDU.JPG&h=19063eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fqiie84rxz7CU0v97rUB_gKzanA=/802x637/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ISGQA5RN3NECTDW4QU4HBS3Z2U.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFqiie84rxz7CU0v97rUB_gKzanA%3D%2F802x637%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FISGQA5RN3NECTDW4QU4HBS3Z2U.JPG&h=98bdb1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aTp-_FrP13oCGG-BOJbcCsUTEyQ=/802x746/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NWUJ26RUDVALHKZWFREXRLUHIY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaTp-_FrP13oCGG-BOJbcCsUTEyQ%3D%2F802x746%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNWUJ26RUDVALHKZWFREXRLUHIY.JPG&h=c97bdfa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210320/RGC3MHZJUNBIRKXC2S23GGETAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210320%2FRGC3MHZJUNBIRKXC2S23GGETAU%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=f7772eed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210320%2FRGC3MHZJUNBIRKXC2S23GGETAU%2F&h=3dd61636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210320/RGC3MHZJUNBIRKXC2S23GGETAU/</a>"},{"pid":"113129a84eea033467d86e670e64ce48b02a6753","tid":2454637,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"男人<im